  "body": [
    "Bhai Takhat Singh Ji, the younger brother of Sant Balwant Singh Ji of Patiala, Punjab, was a respected and renowned Kirtani, especially among the ‘Sangat’ of Delhi. Both brothers were pillars of the Sikh community and were ‘Gurbhais’ of several notable figures, including Bhai Vir Singh Ji, Sant Gurmukh Singh Ji from Patiala, Sant Sangat Singh Ji ‘Kamalia’ and Sant Kartar Singh Ji ‘Kamalia’. Bhai Takhat Singh Ji has also travelled abroad to Iran and Kuwait, where his Kirtan was widely appreciated by the local ‘Sangat’.",
    "The information above was shared by Sahib Singh Bakshi.  If anyone has more information, recordings or photographs of Bhai Takhat Singh Ji, please contact us."
